data.description: **Open House Saturday 11am-1pm** Don’t miss out on this opportunity to own a home that combines comfort, convenience, and character. This beautiful brick ranch is a true gem, perfectly situated in the heart of Sterling Heights.  Imagine the convenience of being close to everything! Whether it’s shopping, dining, or entertainment, this home puts you right in the center of it all. It has been meticulously cared for, from the well-manicured lawn to the spotless interior, you’ll appreciate the attention to detail.With three bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms, there’s room for everyone. Two cars finished with tiles, dry wall, and lighting garage. **UPDATES: Newer roof, newer windows, Water heater 2018, paint and flooring 2020 and more** (Cameras excluded from the sale)
